The paper deals with graph theory and its applications in algorithmic graph structure theory. The main result is the proof of the directed grid theorem, which is a central result in the study of graph minors. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
